scene.message:
Maki: So Chisato was troubled{nl}
too. Somehow I feel{nl}
a lot better now.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: To be petrified at{nl}
such a crucial moment -{nl}
the blunder of a lifetime!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Back together again,{nl}
are they? Well, if the two{nl}
of them are happy, so be it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Were they maybe having{nl}
some really big talk?{nl}
Argh, now I'm curious!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Don't think I'm{nl}
happy about this!{waitkey}{clearbox}Sure, she's not the Sonomura{nl}
from our world, but I'm not{nl}
so low I'd enjoy watching{nl}
someone get their heart broke.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: So there's someone who{nl}
loves you as you are,{nl}
with no need to pretend...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Kozai, hasn't her vibe{nl}
changed? How do I put it -{nl}
she's softened up?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I jotted down Naito's{nl}
lines! Now then, who{nl}
should I use 'em on~{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey, what{nl}
happened while Ayase was{nl}
stuck in stone?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wh-what is it?!{nl}
Ayase isn't crying{nl}
or anything!{waitkey}{ret}

Young Men: Um, excuse me-{nl}
we'd really like to be{nl}
turned back, please...{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: I caused you all{nl}
trouble. This happened{nl}
'cause I wasn't strong enough.{waitkey}I'm sorry.{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: The real Maki is{nl}
shut away in a hospital...{waitkey}{clearbox}Maki's suffering, and yet{nl}
is it all right for{nl}
only me to find happiness?{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Hey, come on~!{nl}
Losing to people like these -{nl}
you're way too weak!{waitkey}{clearbox}Since you lost, I won't{nl}
fix your face for you!{wait_fr:48}{waitkey}{clearbox}Though, you know, I never{nl}
meant to fix it for you{nl}
in the first place~!{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Papa said you're just{nl}
a 'test subject' and a{nl}
'throwaway pawn'!{waitkey}{clearbox}Win or lose, he said{nl}
to just leave you be!{waitkey}{clearbox}So why don't you stay{nl}
like that forever?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
See ya, bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: W-wait...!{nl}
Am I stuck like this{nl}
forever?!{wait_fr:32} ...No...!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Chisato...!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Just hold on, we'll catch{nl}
that girl soon.{waitkey}{clearbox}Then we'll make her put{nl}
your face back the way{nl}
it was!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: Maki...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
You're lying! Don't talk{nl}
nonsense!{wait_fr:16} You think{nl}
I got what I deserved, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yeah!{wait_fr:32}{nl}
You're cheerful, pretty,{nl}
stylish, and so sure{nl}
of yourself.{waitkey}{clearbox}I can see why Naito{nl}
fell for you.{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: That's a lie! Yosuke{nl}
surely{wait_fr:48} still loves Maki{nl}
even now.{wait_fr:69}{nl}
...Maki, I'm sorry.{waitkey}{clearbox}I was jealous of you, Maki.{nl}
Being sure of myself -{nl}
I just made it look{nl}
that way.{waitkey}{clearbox}The real me can't do{nl}
anything. Unless I'm always{nl}
pretty and put-together,{nl}
no one looks my way.{waitkey}{clearbox}So I envied you so much,{nl}
Maki - loved by everyone{nl}
just as you are.{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: After this, Yosuke's{nl}
sure to give up on me.{nl}
Then, Maki, you and{nl}
Yosuke can finally-{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:48}Yosuke...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: You stubborn thing,{nl}
Chisato! You really do{nl}
love Yosuke.{waitkey}{clearbox}But you don't have to{nl}
worry about me...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Because...{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: Chisato...!!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
I finally found you!{nl}
I've been searching all over!{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:48}What happened to{nl}
your face! Are you hurt?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: Maki!{nl}
You're covering for me?{wait_fr:80}{nl}
No... {wait_fr:48}it's fine now!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: Yosuke, look at this!{nl}
This is my face now!{waitkey}{clearbox}I did all sorts of awful{nl}
things, said cruel words{nl}
to Maki.{wait_fr:48}{nl}
This is my punishment!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: I have no right to{nl}
be loved by you, Yosuke!{waitkey}{clearbox}My personality's awful, and{nl}
even the face I was proud{nl}
of has changed...{waitkey}{clearbox}If people saw you with{nl}
someone like me, you'd{nl}
be laughed at too, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}So it's fine now.{nl}
Go to Maki!{nl}
You always loved her, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: Hey, don't get the{nl}
wrong idea!{wait_fr:32}{waitkey}It's true I liked Sonomura{nl}
once, but that's ancient{nl}
history. Now I love only you,{nl}
Chisato!{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:48}Geez, look what you're{nl}
making me say. It's{nl}
embarrassing!{waitkey}Now come on, let's go home!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: But...{wait_fr:80}{nl}
this mole of mine{nl}
will never come off...{waitkey}Are you sure? Even if your{nl}
friends laugh at you...{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: That doesn't matter!{nl}
Let them laugh if they want!{waitkey}{clearbox}You called yourself awful,{nl}
but I've got my ugly sides{nl}
too. You don't always{nl}
have to act prim.{waitkey}{clearbox}Just tell me how you feel{nl}
honestly, like you did{nl}
just now. I'm your boyfriend.{waitkey}{clearbox}Whatever you look like,{nl}
I don't care. Just be{nl}
yourself. I love you,{nl}
Chisato!!{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: Chisato!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Your face{wait_fr:48} - it's back{nl}
to normal!{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: You're right!{wait_fr:64}{nl}
I'm so happy...{wait_fr:80}{nl}
No, not about my face.{waitkey}{clearbox}I always thought Yosuke{nl}
really loved Maki{nl}
deep down...{waitkey}{clearbox}...Thank you...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ahh, that was cramped!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Gah, Naito!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
...Kozai, your mole's{nl}
gone?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmm...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Seems things took a sudden{nl}
turn while I wasn't looking.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Huh, Naito!{nl}
Why are you here?{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Oh, Kozai's mole's{nl}
gone too!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Why's Naito here?{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Oh, Kozai's normal again too!{nl}
Argh, I don't get it!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Naito...?{wait_fr:48}{nl}
So Kozai's back to{nl}
normal too.{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: I'm sorry, Maki.{wait_fr:64}{nl}
I told a lie.{waitkey}{clearbox}Just like you said,{nl}
I really do love Yosuke.{waitkey}{clearbox}I wanted you to forgive me,{waitkey}...{wait_fr:48}but I guess you can't{nl}
anymore. I'd hoped we could{nl}
be best friends again...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Silly!{nl}
There's nothing to forgive!{waitkey}{clearbox}Chisato, you're still my{nl}
best friend.{wait_fr:48} I'm so glad{nl}
for you, Chisato...!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So Aki got away.{waitkey}{clearbox}Kozai, do you know{nl}
anything about a man{nl}
named Kandori?{waitkey}{clearbox}He should be acting{nl}
together with Aki.{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: I don't know anyone{nl}
named Kandori, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}Come to think of it, that{nl}
girl said she lives{nl}
in a castle.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No need to be{nl}
surprised. Child or not,{nl}
Aki's power is immense.{waitkey}Building a castle would{nl}
be easy for her.{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: Chisato, I forgot{nl}
to mention - that Sonomura{nl}
isn't the one we know.{waitkey}{ret}
